; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">4</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA">》是我比较喜欢的一款游戏，还记得当年玩李华梅、或者选赫德拉姆，征服全球海洋时的情景，这两个线路，我都是通关的。而《海洋时代</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">2</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA">》对《大航海时代</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">4</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA">》进行了改良，加入了许多新的元素。反正，你想玩好，就必须打海盗、经商搞海运和探险样样全能；有时候实力不济时，要善于利用他人的力量来完成任务（不过，像我这种较有实力的酱油玩家，某些狭隘的人是不欢迎的），不做任务升级太慢了！</SPAN></FONT></SPAN></DIV>
<div STYLE="pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; MArGin: 0px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left">
<div STYLE="HeiGHT: 0px; CLeAr: both; FonT-siZe: 1px; oVerFLoW: hidden">
<div STYLE="BorDer-BoTToM: #ebebeb 5px solid; BorDer-LeFT: #ebebeb 5px solid; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 27px; MArGin: 0px 0px 10px; pADDinG-LeFT: 10px; WiDTH: 325px; pADDinG-riGHT: 10px; HeiGHT: 37px; CoLor: #26afd9; FonT-siZe: 14px; oVerFLoW: hidden; BorDer-Top: #ebebeb 5px solid; FonT-WeiGHT: bold; BorDer-riGHT: #ebebeb 5px solid; pADDinG-Top: 0px">
网页游戏既耗时间又耗钱!</DIV>
</DIV>
</DIV>
<div STYLE="pADDinG-BoTToM: 16px; Line-HeiGHT: 150%; MArGin: 0px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; FonT-siZe: 12px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"><span STYLE="WorD-WrAp: break-word; CoLor: #666666; WorD-BreAK: break-all"><font COLOR="#000000">
<span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA">
&nbsp;&nbsp;
这种网页游戏就像朋友们介绍的那样，既耗时间又耗钱。呵呵~~有个时候，也身不由己了，谁叫咱好这一口哩？！前几天，好不容易升级到“大公”（公侯伯子男，再大公、摄政王）了，一高兴投了</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">60</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA">块钱到里头，那感觉和不投钱就不一样了，阵型、技能全换了。</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA">这样子，我的航海家拥有1个雷霆2个鼓舞1个精准、2个</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA">坚壁阵、U型、环形阵（比较牛的阵法）和“混乱”技能（能同时攻击</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">5</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA">个点）、“坚固”，杀40级以下海盗如割韭菜般简单了。这个游戏只要拥有“反击”和“雷霆”或者“鼓舞”和“精准”技能基本上可以无敌的，而这些东西，不投钱很难得到的。</SPAN></FONT></SPAN></DIV>
<div STYLE="pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; MArGin: 0px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left">
